<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>There are quite a few code files throughout the library, tests, and incubator that have an inconsistent header docblock.</p>

<p>We need to have a single canonical header docblock that correctly describes the copyright and license for the code, and we need to make that docblock present in all files for PHP code, tests, scripts, etc.</p>

    </div>
